memory_text = "MAGGIE: 'Mum drew one sun because you said the yellow was boring.' A child objects that it has nine rays, not eight. 'Fine. Nine. Put your inhaler inside and do not swap tins with Callum again.' The voice is ordinary enough to hurt."
